Q: When do employees need to submit their timesheets?
A: Timesheets must be submitted by Friday at 5 PM.

Q: How many paid leave days are employees entitled to each year?
A: Employees are entitled to 20 paid leave days per year.

Q: Do work from home requests need approval?
A: Yes, all work from home requests require approval from your manager.

Q: Are employees required to wear ID badges?
A: Yes, employees must wear their ID badges while on company premises.
